high_descs: Turn around and go to the buffet, then turn right and go to the coffee table.
Pick up the gold ornament, to the left of the credit card, on the coffee table.
Turn around and go to the end table across from you.
Place the gold ornament on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put the gold ornament from the coffee table, to the end table.

high_descs: Turn the opposite direction and go to face the left end of the coffee table that is to your right.
Pick up the brass candle holder from the coffee table.
Turn away from the coffee table and move toward the wall.
Put the brass candle holder on the right front corner of the small end table at the wall.
anns.task_desc: Move a brass candle holder from a coffee table to an end table.

high_descs: turn around and move to the center table
pick up the funnel on the table
turn around and head to the stool
place the funnel on the stool
anns.task_desc: place a funnel on a stool
